org.melior.jdbc.core

Class ResultSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.melior.jdbc.core.ResultSet
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    InvocationHandler

    public class ResultSet
extends Object
implements InvocationHandler
    Implements a wrapper around a JDBC ResultSet delegate. The result set writes JDBC timing details to the logs during the lifetime of the result set.
    Since:
    2.2
    Author:
    Melior
